{"tid":1600892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非入] 走唔走自己決定！唔好再做散水撚！","createTime":"2019-09-28T19:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T21:14:10.000Z","uid":48259,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee11aed5b63544052e116e422c33f5c6479884ae","tid":1600892,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T19:31:18.000Z","msg":"今日人多，氣氛好，又有不反對通知書<br />\n唔明點解八點幾就有班人<span style=\"color: red;\">不斷叫無gear嘅人走？！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：防暴喺果邊黎緊啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔好睇啦！唔好做花生友啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你地走咗前線先會走㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：走呀！走啦！走呀！走啦！走呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我乜柒gear都無帶，就係預咗要留到最後<br />\n就算要走都一定係比前線走先！<br />\n我地和理非驚乜鳩？<br />\n就算比狗拉，佢都唔會入到罪<br />\n<br />\n就泥四個月啦<br />\n大家點解仲係要走到逃難咁？<br />\n點解仲未明人愈多就愈安全？<br />\n我地走咗係唔會令前線更安全㗎！<br />\n知唔知每次狂叫人走只會令場面更混亂？<br />\n<br />\n我重申多次：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以後走唔走自己決定<br />\n唔好再做散水撚<br />\n會走嘅人唔洗你講都會走<br />\n唔想走嘅人係唔會比你動搖</span><br />\n<br />\n給前線勇武：<br />\n<strong>你地係矛，唔洗做盾，我地和理非先係盾！</strong><br />\n你地hit完就run，唔洗理我地<br />\n我地見到你地走就會慢慢退<br />\n最後，多謝勇武無私嘅付出！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7825f49dc3b9956a2d1a086d4bc133aa463934","tid":1600892,"uid":62280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"完全認同你所講嘅說話"},{"pid":"c6fb23b5781e94afed6f022281386f62bf75aff9","tid":1600892,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T19:34:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01b70ccaa54b7c6431f03b9771e856e98816c746","tid":1600892,"uid":48259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T19:36:33.000Z","msg":"做個更勇敢嘅和理非好冇？"},{"pid":"807b8c0ccefab468f89df45e1f89f458cb011262